</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing a blue bird in a dream means that the dreamer will go on a journey related to scientific life and therefore will experience separation for a while with the person he loves and each of them will be deeply saddened, but after his return from his journey, he will be happy, and the longing that has exhausted him greatly will disappear.<br/>At the same time, it suggests that the dreamer gets rid of the problems he has been living with for a long time and overcomes his problems, God willing, thanks to the help of a close person or a loved one.</p>
<p>Seeing a sick blue bird in a dream means that the person who sees the dream must separate from the person he loves despite the fact that he is going through a very beautiful period in work life, and for this reason he will live with a wonderful life. He may regret it and spend the rest of his life alone.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the Blue Bird in a Dream by <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></span></h2>
<p>Basically, blue birds in a dream are a symbol of freedom in many places and many things, such as freedom of work or freedom of choosing a spouse and others.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
