</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing a blue bird fluttering in a room or in a cage in a dream means that you are looking for a way out of a confused mental state.<br/>The dream of a beautiful blue bird indicates that your life from the outside looks beautiful and ideal, but in reality you are facing psychological problems and problems that you have not told anyone about.</p>
<p>Anyone who sees blue birds in your dream means that you should not always take them seriously, maybe you should turn a blind eye to some of the words you will hear from people and will not like them.</p>
<p>And the <strong>blue bird in the cage in the dream</strong> can indicate restrictions and lack of freedom and living in illusion and being subjected to obstacles.<br/>An empty cage or a cage with a <strong>dead blue bird in a dream</strong> expresses his disappointment.<br/>Because the blue bird outside the cage shows more freedom in reality, but seeing the blue bird imprisoned in the cage means that it feels very restricted.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
