</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Dreaming of a blue bird indicates breaking boundaries and restrictions, and whoever dreams of it means that he will fight for justice and fight to defend ideas that by their nature need freedom to achieve them.</p>
<p>Seeing a flock of blue birds flying erratically indicates material confusion and mismanagement of money, and it may indicate that the dreamer will stop acting according to his opinion in exchange for acting according to whims and spiritual desire.</p>
<p>Whoever dreams of a blue bird with golden wings indicates longing, and the bird soaring high in the air indicates awareness, civilization, and the person who seeks knowledge.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
