</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p><strong>The small blue bird in a dream</strong> shows the ability to develop your own projects and suggests that you continue to pursue freedom as indicated in seeing it <strong>a baby blue bird in a dream</strong> You need to make plans or preparations to overcome the obstacles you will soon face and move forward towards greater independence.<br/>Blue birds also express people’s need to present their opinions to others.</p>
<p>Seeing a <strong>blue bird nest in a dream</strong> indicates something, a subject, a project, or a person, unfortunately, is not accessible to people and an area that you cannot reach, so you need to make your aspirations and goals realistic and things that you can reach, not unreasonable things or impossible things.<br/>Seeing a blue owl in a dream can symbolize hidden wisdom and the blue crow in a dream represents darkness, sadness, and a sign of bad luck.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-اصطياد-طائر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=34" > Catching a Bird </a> Blue in a Dream</span></h2>
<p>Seeing a <strong>dream of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-اصطياد-طائر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=34" > catching a blue bird </a></strong> shows that the person who saw the dream will face beautiful events related to work life, but he will face psychological pressures and great sadness and will quickly pass this stage and receive important news to do very good deeds soon, and based on this news he will gain very large profits and have a happy and safe marital nest.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
