<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-اصطياد-طائر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=34" > Catching a Bird </a> Blue in a Dream</span></h2>
<p>Seeing <strong>hunting a blue bird in a dream</strong> means that the dreamer will get rid of his worries soon and that the pessimism that he has been living with for a long time in work life will collapse soon and he will participate in a profitable business with one of his relatives or with a friend or wife, and he will sign very successful and large projects, and he will get very large profits and gain experience in work that will raise him forward and he will be appointed to good positions at the highest levels.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of Feeding the Blue Bird in a Dream</span></h2>
<p>Seeing <strong>feeding a blue bird in a dream</strong> expresses that the person who sees the dream will have very bad days in work life, but despite this situation, he will provide support to the people close to him and whom he cares about, and for this he will receive blessings and these people will do so. Help him when he sees very bad days and there will be a very great bond between him and those around him.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of a Dead Blue Bird in a Dream</span></h2>
<p>Seeing a dead blue bird in a dream means disappointment and displeasure, but it also shows bitterness for someone who suddenly no longer relies on us.<br/>Also, seeing the death of the blue bird in …</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
