</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>If you are eating mussels in a dream, it means that you are entering a period of joy and prosperity, and if you are eating mussels in the presence of your life partner, it may be a sign that you will have many children.<br/>If you are enjoying eating mussels with friends or other loved ones, it is a sign of joy and happiness and may mean that someone close to you will be stubborn or determined to cause problems with you or cause a situation that worries you.</p>
<p>Finding mussels in your dream in this case, mussels symbolize happy or peaceful times.<br/>If someone gave you mussels, this happiness and peace will be somehow related to the person who gave you the mussels.<br/>If this person gave you a gift or took you out to eat mussels, it means that they appreciate you and enjoy having you in their life.<br/>This means that this person holds you in high esteem and will do everything in their power to make you feel happy, safe, and loved.</p>
<p>But if you find an empty <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-بلح-البحر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=15" > mussel </a> shell in a dream, it may mean that you will lose something very important to you.<br/>But if you open the mussels and find them empty inside, this means that you will lose, or that you have recently suffered a loss in your life.<br/>If you go out to eat mussels with a group of people and one of the mussels on your plate is empty, this may be a sign that someone close to you has betrayed you or will harm you or betray you in the future.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
