<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-بلح-البحر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=15" > Mussels </a> in a dream can indicate harm, as surfers were injured by a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-بلح-البحر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=15" > mussel </a> shell.<br/>Being injured by a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-بلح-البحر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=15" > mussel </a> shell and feeling pain in a dream, especially if there is blood, is a sign of the need for healing.  As it is likely that there will be many problems in your life in the future, dreams of being injured by a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-بلح-البحر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=15" > mussel </a> shell often indicate the need for emotional healing.</p>
