<p><span></span></p>
<p>And to indicate the following, the hadith sent.  About Aslam, the slave of Omar:</p>
<p>When Noah entered the ark, two of every pair said: How can we be sure, or how can the animals be sure that the lion is with us?  So God gave him a fever, and it was the first fever that descended upon the earth.  Narrated by Ibn Kathir.</p>
<p>And the meaning of seeing a lion in a dream can be an indication of a journey that changes the color of his skin to brown.  This is due to the possibility of extraction and exhaustion, so blackness and lion, individually and collectively, have similarities in wording.<br/>The dream of the lion can be among its meanings that accompany those who do not master them, hard-hearted and those with unrestrained temperaments, and this is due to the connection between the ferocity of the lion and its nature and its nature. reaching the vision.<br/>The presence of the lion in your dream may indicate the presence of a contagious disease or epidemic that needs to be warned and taken care of, and consider the following hadith narrated by al-Bukhari in Sahih from the authority of Abu Hurayrah, may Allah be pleased with him, saying: The Messenger of Allah, peace be upon him, said: No filth, no bird, no important, no yellow, flee from the leper as you flee from the lion.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
