<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/رؤية-الأسد-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=578" > a lion </a> may indicate harsh words and a sharp tongue, look at the hadith below to understand the connection between this meaning and this symbol.<br/>It was narrated that the Prophet, peace be upon him, was angry with Quraysh and ordered them to be lampooned.  “It is more difficult for them than for the nobles to strike them.  So he sent Ibn Ruwahah and said: Shake them.  So they shook them, and they were not satisfied.  So he sent to Ka’b bin Malik.  Then he sent to Hasan bin Thabit.  When he came to him, Hasan said: It is time to send this lion who whips his tail.  Then he stuck out his tongue and moved it.  He said: To whom did you send with the truth!  To the skin, pour them out empty of the idol.  The Messenger of Allah, peace be upon him, said: Do not rush.  Abu Bakr is the most knowledgeable of Quraysh about their lineage.  And I have their ancestors.  So to summarize it for you.  Hasan missed him.  Then he turned and said: O Messenger of Allah!  Your lineage has been summarized for me.  He is the one who sent you with the truth!  I will bring you out of them like a hair from dough.  Aisha said: I heard the Messenger of Allah, peace be upon him, say to Hasan: The Holy Spirit supports you as long as you are praying for Allah and His Messenger.  He said: I heard the Messenger of Allah, peace be upon him, say: Hasan has healed them, so he was healed and healed.  Hasan said:</p>
<p>I lampooned Muhammad, and I answered him, and by Allah in this reward<br/>I lampooned Muhammad the just, the Messenger of Allah, his faith<br/>My father is his father, and my honor is with the honor of Muhammad, may you be protected<br/>My daughter, I apologize if she does not see her stirring the dates from my hand like a disease<br/>They compare the bleating with the elevator, on their shoulders the thirsty donkey<br/>Our horses are constantly raining, and women fill them with wine<br/>If you stay away from us, we will perform the Umrah, and the opening and the cover<br/>Otherwise, be patient with the strike of the day when Allah honors whomever He wills<br/>And Allah said: I have sent a servant who speaks with truth without concealment<br/>And Allah said: An army of ease is the Ansar, I have shown it to meet him<br/>Every day we have insults or quarrels or lampoons<br/>So who mocked you, the Messenger of Allah, praised him and supported him<br/>And Gabriel, the Messenger of Allah, is among us, and the Holy Spirit is incomparable</p>
<p>The Prophet, peace be upon him, said: You were healed, O Hasan, and you were healed.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
