</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Among the meanings that I prefer in this symbol is the existence of a service that is given to the vision by an influential person, such as princes and ministers, for example.  And the word “lion” can be compared to our saying: “A lion makes a favor.”  Think about it to discover the relationship between what I said and what I concluded.</p>
<p>It also has good meanings, especially when seen in winter: improving the health of the viewer and the disappearance of the symptoms of the disease that afflicts humans, especially in winter, such as influenza, for example.</p>
<p>In addition to that, among its meanings is the existence of an enemy who controls it according to his condition, especially for the oppressed, so beware of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/رؤية-الأسد-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=578" > seeing a lion </a> in a dream, for behind it. It is a call to the oppressed.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
