<p>Seeing yourself holding a friend's hand in a dream indicates your desire for the friend and your longing for a relationship. There are other interpretations that we will explain for single girls, married women, <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant women </a>, divorced women, and how you held your friend's hand, or your friend held your hand and left, or you held your friend's hand by <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a>, and more in the continuation of the topic:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of holding a friend's hand in a dream</span></h2>
<p>If you dream of holding a friend's hand, this dream may reveal some of your fears about that person, meaning that this dream may reveal your fears of distancing yourself from that person or that person distancing himself from you, and you may fear for your friendship. and his future.</p>
<p>In some cases, this dream symbolizes your loneliness and feelings of isolation from others, as well as your desire for intimacy or connection with your friends.<br/>The dream of holding your friend's hand reflects your fear of losing those close to you, and you are afraid that your loved ones will one day separate from you, and you are afraid of being alone and isolated in life as your fear.  Rejection in life drives you to close yourself off in a bubble where you try not to maintain a secure emotional attachment to others, but you still want to keep them close.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
