</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing yourself holding a friend's hand while fighting with him in a dream means that you will reconcile with him in the future, and some events or situations will lead you to resolve the problems between you and give up the differences or problems that you have with each other, the problems between you will be resolved and you may be friends with each other in the end after you leave all the hatred and you will feel less weight after removing all the toxic feelings from your mind.</p>
<p>Holding a friend's hand is a sign of the continuous love between you and him, and a sign of intimacy, lasting love, and love for sharing most things with this friend.</p>
<p>And if you are a woman and you are clinging to a friend in your dream, you may be grateful for the presence of this person in your life because he is one of those rare friends who support you no matter what and maintains a good relationship with you.  With him and strengthen your relationship with him.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
