<h2><span>Interpretation of holding a friend's hand in a dream by <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></span></h2>
<p>Seeing <strong><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-تمسك-يد-الصديق-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=15" > holding a friend's hand </a> in a dream</strong>, whoever holds the hand of a friend in the dream will see material and moral support from those who love him, and he will overcome his difficult days thanks to them.<br/>In addition, the dreamer will advance in his knowledge and experience in the situations of the case as if he were a government official, and this indicates that these circumstances that he is going through will make him many supporters.<br/>And look at the single girl <strong>a friend holding her brother's hand in a dream</strong>, this indicates the strong friendship between the mother and her friend.</p>
<p>And holding the hand of a friend in general indicates help and support, or that you will provide help to others.</p>
<p>Regarding <strong>dreaming of holding the hand of a severed friend</strong>, this is a sign of the death of the sister or friend.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
