</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of holding a friend's hand in a dream</span></h2>
<p>To dream that you are holding the hand of your current girlfriend is a romantic dream that suggests that there may be a strong emotional attraction.  Although commitment is not always necessary, this dream may indicate that you will share with this partner on a compassionate level and fulfill all the promises you made, you have done so with this person.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of holding a friend's hand in a dream for a man</span></h2>
<p>If a man sees himself holding the hand of his friend in a dream, this indicates the strength of his relationship with this friend and a sign of the improvement of the viewer's financial situation and overcoming all his problems.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
