</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of holding a friend's hand in a dream for a pregnant woman</span></h2>
<p>Seeing a friend holding a friend's hand in a pregnant woman's dream indicates a smooth pregnancy path and a sign of an imminent birth of the fetus.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of holding a friend's hand in a dream for a married woman</span></h2>
<p>If a married woman sees herself holding the hand of her friend in a dream, this indicates the end of problems, overcoming crises, and living a happy life.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
