</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>Anyone who sees himself holding the hand of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شخص-ما-في-المنام?page=2395" > someone </a> in a dream, the dream reflects your desire to feel protected and secure by surrounding yourself with people you trust and rely on completely.<br/>The dream in which you are holding the hand of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شخص-ما-في-المنام?page=2395" > someone </a> indicates your desire to have a friend or partner with whom you can share all your secrets and problems.</p>
<p>Dreams of holding hands have positive implications and symbolize reconciliation and friendship or the desire to feel love and protection, and God knows best.</p>
